abstract: The lawyer said she was trying to follow her client, an undocumented 3-year-old boy, into an agency building in Kansas City, Mo., to reunite him with his mother before they were deported.
snippet: The lawyer said she was trying to follow her client, an undocumented 3-year-old boy, into an agency building in Kansas City, Mo., to reunite him with his mother before they were deported.
lead_paragraph: An immigration lawyer said she fractured her foot after being pushed to the ground by an Immigration and Customs Enforcement officer as she followed her client, a 3-year-old boy, into an ICE building in Kansas City, Mo.

abstract: A stellar outing by Luis Severino gave the Yankees another easy win on the road. A savvy slide by Austin Romine provided some laughs.
snippet: A stellar outing by Luis Severino gave the Yankees another easy win on the road. A savvy slide by Austin Romine provided some laughs.
lead_paragraph: PHILADELPHIA — As Austin Romine took off for third on a wild pitch, he was greeted by a worrying sight when he peeked toward home plate — the ball had ricocheted off the brick wall behind home plate and bounced right back to Phillies catcher Andrew Knapp.

abstract: The process to choose a developer to build a lucrative solar panel plant in Buffalo was rigged to favor his firm, an ex-executive of the firm testified.
snippet: The process to choose a developer to build a lucrative solar panel plant in Buffalo was rigged to favor his firm, an ex-executive of the firm testified.
lead_paragraph: The chance to build a solar panel manufacturing plant in Buffalo was billed as one of the most exciting projects upstate in years and, by extension, a highly coveted opportunity for developers vying for the state contract worth hundreds of millions of dollars.

abstract: For Gov. Andrew M. Cuomo and Cynthia Nixon, the Pride parade offered a stage for the Democratic primary. It’s not clear that anyone noticed.
snippet: For Gov. Andrew M. Cuomo and Cynthia Nixon, the Pride parade offered a stage for the Democratic primary. It’s not clear that anyone noticed.
lead_paragraph: The governor brought a hulking tractor-trailer with confetti guns, thousands upon thousands of rainbow-printed signs and a coterie of elected officials. His Democratic challenger brought a modest pickup truck with glittery blue tassels, a small but vigorous musical quartet and Lea DeLaria, an actress from the television show “Orange Is the New Black.”

abstract: With a 2-1 victory over South Korea, Mexico is in a strong position to advance to the round of 16. And Coach Juan Carlos Osorio is no longer being derided.

lead_paragraph: ROSTOV-ON-DON, Russia — The singing started in the dying minutes of the match. Like so many chants that pop up these days in international soccer, it cribbed the familiar bass line of the White Stripes song “Seven Nation Army.”
